#-Function--color.set
  Function: color.set
      Desc: turn on/off colorized output from msg* functions.
          : color is turned off if verbose() is also set to off.
  Synopsis: color.set [on|1] | [off|0]
          : curstatus=$(color.set)
   Example: color.set off
          : status=$(color.set)
#-Function--color.set---------------------------------------------------------
